WEBVTT

00:00:58.720 --> 00:01:02.960
ML: "Don't worry, you won't be fired,
but you'll slowly be weeded out."

00:01:03.800 --> 00:01:07.480
And then he laughed and lots of others
on their team laughed as well,

00:01:08.920 --> 00:01:11.776
but it was completely apparent
that it wasn't a joke.

00:01:11.800 --> 00:01:15.400
AG: People got fired
for having the wrong personality.

00:01:16.160 --> 00:01:22.456
(Music)

00:01:22.480 --> 00:01:24.736
I'm Adam Grant and this is WorkLife,

00:01:24.760 --> 00:01:26.696
my podcast with TED.

00:01:26.720 --> 00:01:28.616
I'm an organizational psychologist.

00:01:28.640 --> 00:01:30.880
I study how to make work not suck.